BLOCKSWORLD.name: on
BLOCKSWORLD.true_func: function (id, o1, o2) {        return {            id: id,            x: o2.x,            y: o2.y - 40        }    }
BLOCKSWORLD.false_func: function (id, o1, o2) {        return {            id: id        }    }

BLOCKSWORLD.name: ontable
BLOCKSWORLD.true_func: function (id, o1) {        const idToOrder = {"a": 1, "b": 2, "c": 3, "d": 4, "e": 5, "f": 6, "g": 7, "h": 8, "i": 9, "j": 10};        return {            id: id,            x: 40 + (idToOrder[id] ? idToOrder[id] : Math.floor(Math.random() * 5)) * 40,            y: 400        }    }

BLOCKSWORLD.name: holding
BLOCKSWORLD.true_func: function (id, o1) {        return {            id: id,            x: 600,            y: 100        }    }

GRIPPER.name: room
GRIPPER.true_func: function (id, o1) {        const rooms = {"a": 1, "b": 2};        return {            id: id,            x: 100 + rooms[id] ? (rooms[id]) * 200 : Math.random() * 200,            y: 500        }    }

GRIPPER.name: ball
GRIPPER.false_func: function (id, o1, o2) {        return {            id: id        }    }

GRIPPER.name: at
GRIPPER.true_func: function (id, o1, o2) {        return {            id: id,            x: o2.x,            y: o2.y        }    }
GRIPPER.false_func: function (id, o1, o2) {        return {            id: id        }    }

GRIPPER.name: gripper
GRIPPER.true_func: function (id, o1) {        const grippers = {"left": 1, "right": 2};        return {            id: id,            x: 400 + grippers[id] ? grippers[id] * 100 : (Math.random() * 300),            y: 100        }    }

GRIPPER.name: carry
GRIPPER.true_func: function (id, o1, o2) {        return [{            id: id,            x: o1.x,            y: o1.y - 100        }, {            id: o2.id,            x: o1.x,            y: o1.y - 150        }]    }
GRIPPER.false_func: function (id, o1, o2) {        return {            id: id        }    }
